## Connection & Troubleshooting

Before generating, always check server health:
```
GET /api/health
```
Verify `models_loaded: true` and note `active_model`. If models aren't loaded, wait — the server is still initializing.

The server port (`65241`) is assigned at startup. If LTX Desktop restarts, the port may change — check the app's logs.

Only one generation runs at a time. If a previous gen is stuck, cancel it before submitting:
```
POST /api/generate/cancel
```
